1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,640
Llevo semanas

2
00:00:00,640 --> 00:00:01,560
viendo algo...

3
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:02,360
y cada día

4
00:00:02,360 --> 00:00:02,800
va a más.

5
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:03,080
Gente por

6
00:00:03,080 --> 00:00:03,760
toda España

7
00:00:03,760 --> 00:00:04,440
publicando lo que

8
00:00:04,440 --> 00:00:05,320
les sobra.

9
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:05,960
Sin pedir nada

10
00:00:05,960 --> 00:00:06,680
a cambio.

11
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:07,960
Sin esperar nada.

12
00:00:07,960 --> 00:00:09,080
Solo compartir.

13
00:00:09,080 --> 00:00:09,920
Y al otro lado...

14
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:11,000
alguien lo descubre.

15
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:11,880
Mismo barrio.

16
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:12,720
Misma zona.

17
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:13,240
Sin haberse

18
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:14,360
cruzado nunca.

19
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:15,080
Y de repente...

20
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:16,360
conectan.

21
00:00:16,360 --> 00:00:16,600
Eso es

22
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:17,320
lo que estamos

23
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,040
viendo.

24
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:18,640
No es una moda.

25
00:00:18,640 --> 00:00:19,320
Es gente real

26
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:20,000
haciendo algo

27
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:20,760
que tiene sentido.

28
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:22,040
Personas que dan.

29
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:23,400
Personas que encuentran.

30
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:25,000
Sin complicaciones.

31
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:25,960
Y esto...

32
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:26,920
va creciendo.

33
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:27,400
Givore.

34
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:28,200
Si os sobra

35
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:28,680
algo en casa...

36
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:29,520
compartidlo.

37
00:00:29,520 --> 00:00:30,520
Así de simple.

